{"tid":1520662,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[葵涌斬警察其實係高招？]","createTime":"2019-08-31T02:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T02:57:20.000Z","uid":160294,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a27800375b006868ce108f1d8355064a43534957","tid":1520662,"uid":160294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:13:17.000Z","msg":"利申 : 核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\nTLDR<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">斬來唔係比市民睇，係比警察睇。</span></span></strong><br />\n諗下721之後幾多人想燒村？<br />\n同一個道理用番落警察上面，佢地今日更加出師有名，無心理負擔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(唔同情況？你覺得毅進仔有自己獨立思考？)<br />\n(斬警察都唔斬何妖，前線有邊個警察唔可以被犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n高係邊？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">就係唔可以確定係唔係邊個做<br />\n各有各講。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>激發警察，令佢地更無心理負擔個作用就已經收到。</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>今日啲警察失控既情況會更加嚴重。加埋拉晒和理非非議員，無左道緩衝.....<br />\n成個局就係住死裏打。</em></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點做好？<br />\n局就set好，入唔入局，點破局靠大家。<br />\nBe water. 同班癲狗鬥力好蝕章。"},{"pid":"7806a270e98cc0c54030b0878e627022bad82b3d","tid":1520662,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:13:31.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會 港島見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=